Nada
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Poco
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Medio
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 o 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Mucho
\shape default

\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

.
